  {
    "id": "s1_2_halves",
    "steps": [
      [
        {
          "type": "scene",
          "method": "add",
          "tangible_id": "bar",
          "tangible_type": "NumLine",
          "params": {
            "visual": "bar",
            "lcm": 4,
            "description": "Empty whole bar appears."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "Good. Now let's split the bar into two. Click right in the middle to make two equal parts."
        },
        {
          "type": "prompt",
          "text": "Click once in the middle to split the bar into 2 equal parts.",
          "tool": { "name": "place" },
          "target": "bar",
          "validator": [
            {
              "condition": { "ticks": ["0/2", "1/2", "2/2"] },
              "description": "Student placed a cut at the midpoint, creating 2 equal halves.",
              "is_correct": true,
              "steps": [
                [
                  {
                    "type": "dialogue",
                    "text": "Yes. You made two equal parts: two halves. See how each part is exactly the same size?"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "current_scene",
                    "elements": [
                      {
                        "tangible_id": "bar",
                        "tangible_type": "NumLine",
                        "description": "Bar partitioned into 2 equal halves.",
                        "visual": "bar",
                        "intervals": "1/2"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "current_scene",
          "elements": [
            {
              "tangible_id": "bar",
              "tangible_type": "NumLine",
              "description": "Empty whole bar. Place tool active.",
              "visual": "bar"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "Now click one of those parts to shade it."
        },
        {
          "type": "prompt",
          "text": "Click on 1 of the 2 parts to shade it.",
          "tool": { "name": "paint" },
          "target": "bar",
          "validator": [
            {
              "condition": { "shaded": "1/2" },
              "description": "Student shaded 1 of 2 equal parts.",
              "is_correct": true,
              "steps": [
                [
                  {
                    "type": "dialogue",
                    "text": "Yes. You selected one part out of two equal parts."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "current_scene",
                    "elements": [
                      {
                        "tangible_id": "bar",
                        "tangible_type": "NumLine",
                        "description": "Bar partitioned into halves. One half shaded.",
                        "visual": "bar",
                        "intervals": "1/2"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "current_scene",
          "elements": [
            {
              "tangible_id": "bar",
              "tangible_type": "NumLine",
              "description": "Bar partitioned into 2 halves. Paint tool active.",
              "visual": "bar",
              "intervals": "1/2"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "When we split something into equal parts we make all the parts the same size. That's important for what we're learning about fractions. To make equal parts, some kids picture folding the shape, while others might measure it in their mind to check if the parts match. Think about how you did it."
        },
        {
          "type": "current_scene",
          "elements": [
            {
              "tangible_id": "bar",
              "tangible_type": "NumLine",
              "description": "Bar partitioned into halves. One half shaded.",
              "visual": "bar",
              "intervals": "1/2"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "scene",
          "method": "add",
          "tangible_id": "vocab_partitioning",
          "tangible_type": "vocab_card",
          "params": {
            "label": "Partitioning",
            "description": "Vocab card for Partitioning appears."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "When mathematicians divide something into equal parts like you just did, they call it PARTITIONING. You partitioned the bar into two equal parts. Partition is our special math word for dividing one whole into equal-sized sections."
        },
        {
          "type": "current_scene",
          "elements": [
            {
              "tangible_id": "bar",
              "tangible_type": "NumLine",
              "description": "Bar partitioned into halves. One half shaded.",
              "visual": "bar",
              "intervals": "1/2"
            },
            {
              "tangible_id": "vocab_partitioning",
              "tangible_type": "vocab_card",
              "description": "Vocab card: Partitioning.",
              "label": "Partitioning"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    ]
